      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/544113488_18421603861106943_272340255600313209_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcxNzY5NTM2OTY5MTA0NzgzMA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTM1MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=-1jNet6rfXwQ7kNvwGvzrxx&amp;_nc_oc=Ado_sIrM_nSyGmyHDkVhmyv4yCer8YQd1pDcUr_Gu_RZ0K-C9fTQiBU8wzG--NVTPbI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=QXSQP1MmvVbyo9lze9BNhA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxE3FvUZ8CQYI9Q0w9ZUEGXRp-WYIGlXWjx2QHFYRTYNA&amp;oe=69CA26E3" alt="Slide 1 fra @pjharveyofficial" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/542906005_18421603873106943_9087842915161562119_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcxNzY5NTM2OTY5MTAwNjk5NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHg5MDAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=0biOFBRrZ2cQ7kNvwG8UrOI&amp;_nc_oc=AdqE36Su5FIzLg4xKfd_Ar5oiRfNcUt335gw3svRz4E_Sh8qfNw2lu86l_TX2FuiUg8&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=QXSQP1MmvVbyo9lze9BNhA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyCgGxb7LPz87Rc6DjNQtkL6mGvwTIuP8wNVtLD3Z39CA&amp;oe=69CA14FB" alt="Slide 2 fra @pjharveyofficial" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (2 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@pjharveyofficial</strong></p><p>PJ Harvey collaborator and friend @murphyseamus3 has released his latest book ‘Strange Love’ and appears on Tyler Cowen’s ‘Conversations with Tyler’ podcast. <br/>
<br/>
In this interview he talks about his journey as a photographer and filmmaker, and speaks about his work with PJ Harvey on both the ‘Let England Shake’ and ‘The Hope Six Demolition Project’ albums. <br/>
<br/>
‘Strange Love’ is out now.</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DOYCwyNjCyD/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
